{"type":"message","id":"c66565b5","parentId":"ce7e9a9e","timestamp":"2026-03-18T13:44:45.269Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从日志里看到了关键信息：\n\n```\n[info]: [\n  '[ws]',\n  'receive events or callbacks through persistent connection only available in self-build & Feishu app, Configured in:\\n' +\n    '        Developer Console(开发者后台) \\n' +\n    '          ->\\n' +\n    '        Events and Callbacks(事件与回调)\\n' +\n    '          -> \\n' +\n    '        Mode of event/callback subscription(订阅方式)\\n' +\n    '          -> \\n' +\n    '        Receive events/callbacks through persistent connection(使用 长连接 接收事件/回调)'\n]\n```\n\n这说明飞书应用需要配置\"事件订阅\"才能接收消息！这是一个关键问题。\n\n另外，所有4个飞书账号（main, coder, newsai, pm）都显示 \"running\"，说明 WebSocket 连接已经建立。但问题在于飞书应用没有正确配置事件订阅。\n\n我需要告诉用户在飞书开放平台配置事件订阅。","thinkingSignature":"5dc063636b2dcee8da44459889ba4998ae8ca8dfb310193fe8d7da82c89dfcd5"},{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了！\n\n从日志看到关键提示：\n\n```\nreceive events or callbacks through persistent connection only available in self-build & Feishu app\n```\n\n**PM 飞书应用缺少\"事件订阅\"配置！**\n\n请在飞书开放平台配置：\n\n1. 进入 PM 应用 → **应用能力 → 事件订阅**\n2. **订阅方式**：选择「使用长连接接收事件/回调」\n3. 添加事件：`im.message.receive_v1`（接收消息）\n4. 保存并发布\n\n配置好后再试一次发消息给我。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":81910,"output":321,"cacheRead":38823,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121054,"cost":{"input":0.024572999999999998,"output":0.0003852,"cacheRead":0.00116469,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.026122889999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773841456861}}
